social_posts.post_text: florida was goood it was good

wow it’s been one year since i decided to be comfortable in my body.. can’t believe it’s been that long.. at the same time it also feels like i’ve always belonged here; at peace. the progress from the last two pictures blows my mind. So much has happened between then and now, being faced with new challenges and learning who in my life actually shows up for me, and loves me for exactly who i am has been a huge (difficult) necessary blessing. i still have much to learn but it feels so good to be here at the beginning. I wouldn’t have it any other way. 🥲❤️

you have nowhere left to go or to be seen because who wants to live in a place that doesn’t want you back but you still try to fit in. fake it. because of fear that it’s true or hope that you’re wrong. how long can you fake it until you make it out alive or past whatever your heart tells you is too much?what is too much? if it was more than enough i could feel it and tell you but i cant. i only know conditional things where one has to fit to stay.
